speech: You can directly get the test done at any of the government approved laboratories based on a valid prescription of a registered medical practitioner. Once the tests are done, share with us the bills and prescription/Form 44 and we will reimburse the amount to you. Please note that the limit up to which we will reimburse is mentioned in your Welcome Kit. You can get reimbursement by uploading the invoice on the Bajaj Finserv Health App, or sending the invoice via Email on our customer care ID. Once verified, the amount shall be credited into your bank account within 2-3 business days.
